+## Sprint Contract — Round 1
+**Status**: `approved`
+
+### Scope
+基于 spec 需求实现以下变更: [LONG-TERM KNOWLEDGE RECALL — 向量语义检索]
+
+- [2026-04-11 17:02] [SPEC] [VACCINE WARNING] [LONG-TERM KNOWLEDGE RECALL]
