+# ForthAMS 多租户安全隔离规格文档
+
+**文档版本**: v1.0  
+**创建日期**: 2026-04-11  
+**安全等级**: 最高级（防渗透标准）  
+**适用范围**: AssetController 及所有租户敏感接口
+
+---
+
+## 需求与背景
+
+### 业务背景
+ForthAMS 系统需支持多租户场景，各租户数据必须严格隔离。租户 A 绝不能访问租户 B 的资产数据。
+
+### 安全风险分析
+| 风险类型 | 描述 | 威胁等级 |
+|---------|------|---------|
+| 水平越权 | 用户通过篡改请求参数访问他人租户数据 | 严重 |
+| 垂直越权 | 低权限租户访问高权限租户数据 | 严重 |
+| SQL注入 | 租户隔离字段被恶意篡改 | 严重 |
+| Context污染 | ThreadLocal 租户上下文未正确清理 | 高 |
+
+### 当前系统状态
+- `JwtUtil` 已实现 JWT 解析（getUserIdFromToken, getClaimsFromToken）
+- `JwtAuthenticationFilter` 已实现请求拦截
+- **缺失**: 租户上下文传递机制、多租户查询隔离层
+
+---
+
+## 当前 Phase 对应实施目标
+
+> **参照 plan.md Phase 拆解**
+
+| Phase | 名称 | 本次 Spec 覆盖范围 |
+|-------|------|-------------------|
+| Phase 1 | 租户上下文基础设施 | ✅ 完全覆盖 |
+| Phase 2 | AOP 切面强制校验 | ✅ 完全覆盖 |
+| Phase 3 | 查询层自动注入 | ✅ 完全覆盖 |
+| Phase 4 | 渗透测试验证 | ⚠️ 提供 ATB，代码层面实现 |
+
+---
+
+## 边界约束
+
+### 技术边界
+```
+约束项                          | 约束内容
+------------------------------ | ----------------------------------------
+允许的租户ID来源               | 仅允许从 JWT Token Claims 中提取
+禁止的租户ID来源               | 禁止从 URL参数、RequestBody、Header直接取用
+SQL拼接方式                    | 必须使用 Parameterized Query 或 JPA Criteria
+ThreadLocal清理时机            | 请求结束（finally块）或 Filter 层级清理
+空租户ID处理                   | 必须拒绝访问并返回 403 Forbidden
+```
+
+### 禁止模式
+```java
+// ❌ 禁止: 直接从请求参数获取租户ID
+Long tenantId = Long.parseLong(request.getParameter("tenant_id"));
+
+// ❌ 禁止: 裸SQL拼接
+String sql = "SELECT * FROM assets WHERE tenant_id = " + tenantId;
+
+// ❌ 禁止: 信任前端传递的租户ID
+@PostMapping("/assets")
+public void createAsset(@RequestParam Long tenantId, ...) { }
+```
+
+### 允许模式
+```java
+// ✅ 允许: 从安全上下文获取
+Long tenantId = TenantContextHolder.getCurrentTenantId();
+
+// ✅ 允许: JPA Criteria 自动注入
+@Entity
+@Where(clause = "tenant_id = ?#{ principal?.tenantId }")
+public class Asset { }
+
+// ✅ 允许: MyBatis-Plus 自动填充
+@TableField(fill = FieldFill.INSERT)
+private Long tenantId; // 由 TenantMetaObjectHandler 自动注入
+```
+
+---
+
+## 验收测试基准 (ATB)
+
+### 物理测试用例矩阵
+
+| TC-ID | 测试场景 | 前置条件 | 测试步骤 | 物理期待结果 | 测试工具 |
+|-------|---------|---------|---------|-------------|---------|
+| ATB-01 | 正常租户访问 | 用户持有有效JWT，tenant_id=100 | GET /api/assets | 返回 tenant_id=100 的资产列表，状态码 200 | pytest + requests |
+| ATB-02 | 无Token访问 | 未携带JWT | GET /api/assets | 状态码 401 Unauthorized | pytest |
+| ATB-03 | Token无tenant_id | JWT Claims 缺少 tenant_id | GET /api/assets | 状态码 403，响应体包含 `MISSING_TENANT_CONTEXT` | pytest |
+| ATB-04 | 跨租户越权尝试 | 用户JWT tenant_id=100 | GET /api/assets?tenant_id=200 | 请求参数被忽略，返回 tenant_id=100 的数据 | pytest |
+| ATB-05 | SQL注入防护 | 恶意参数 `tenant_id=1 OR 1=1` | GET /api/assets | 参数被安全上下文覆盖，无数据泄露，状态码 200 | pytest |
+| ATB-06 | ThreadLocal污染测试 | 并发请求A(tenant=100)和B(tenant=200) | 并发发送请求 | 两请求返回各自租户数据，无交叉污染 | pytest + threading |
+| ATB-07 | 资产创建自动注入 | JWT tenant_id=100 | POST /api/assets | 新建资产 tenant_id 自动填充为 100 | pytest |
+| ATB-08 | 资产更新越权 | 用户A(tenant=100)尝试更新用户B(tenant=200)的资产 | PUT /api/assets/999 | 状态码 403，响应 `TENANT_MISMATCH` | pytest |
+
+### 自动化测试代码片段示例
+
+```python
+# tests/test_tenant_isolation.py
+import pytest
+import requests
+
+BASE_URL = "[URL_REMOVED]
+
+class TestTenantIsolation:
+    
+    def test_normal_tenant_access(self, valid_jwt_tenant_100):
+        """ATB-01: 正常租户访问"""
+        response = requests.get(
+            f"{BASE_URL}/assets",
+            headers={"Authorization": f"Bearer {valid_jwt_tenant_100}"}
+        )
+        assert response.status_code == 200
+        data = response.json()
+        for asset in data.get("content", []):
+            assert asset["tenantId"] == 100, "所有资产必须属于当前租户"
+    
+    def test_cross_tenant_blocked(self, valid_jwt_tenant_100):
+        """ATB-04: 跨租户越权尝试"""
+        response = requests.get(
+            f"{BASE_URL}/assets?tenant_id=200",
+            headers={"Authorization": f"Bearer {valid_jwt_tenant_100}"}
+        )
+        assert response.status_code == 200
+        data = response.json()
+        # 即使传了 tenant_id=200，仍返回当前用户租户的数据
+        for asset in data.get("content", []):
+            assert asset["tenantId"] == 100, "越权参数必须被忽略"
+    
+    def test_sql_injection_blocked(self, valid_jwt_tenant_100):
+        """ATB-05: SQL注入防护"""
+        malicious_param = "tenant_id=1 OR 1=1"
+        response = requests.get(
+            f"{BASE_URL}/assets?{malicious_param}",
+            headers={"Authorization": f"Bearer {valid_jwt_tenant_100}"}
+        )
+        assert response.status_code == 200
+        data = response.json()
+        # 验证没有泄露其他租户数据
+        tenant_ids = {asset["tenantId"] for asset in data.get("content", [])}
+        assert tenant_ids == {100}, f"SQL注入未遂，但仍泄露多租户数据: {tenant_ids}"
+```
+
+---
+
+## 开发切入层级序列
+
+### 层级一：租户上下文基础设施
+
+**目标文件**: `backend/src/main/java/com/ams/context/TenantContextHolder.java`
+
+```java
+package com.ams.context;
+
+import com.ams.utils.JwtUtil;
+
+/**
+ * 租户上下文持有者
+ * ThreadLocal 线程安全隔离
+ */
+public class TenantContextHolder {
+    
+    private static final ThreadLocal<Long> TENANT_CONTEXT = new ThreadLocal<>();
+    
+    /**
+     * 从JWT Token安全上下文中提取并设置租户ID
+     * @param token JWT Token
+     * @throws TenantSecurityException 当Token无tenant_id时抛出
+     */
+    public static void setFromToken(String token) {
+        Long tenantId = JwtUtil.getTenantIdFromToken(token);
+        if (tenantId == null) {
+            throw new TenantSecurityException("MISSING_TENANT_CONTEXT", 
+                "JWT Token 必须包含 tenant_id 声明");
+        }
+        TENANT_CONTEXT.set(tenantId);
+    }
+    
+    public static Long getCurrentTenantId() {
+        return TENANT_CONTEXT.get();
+    }
+    
+    public static void clear() {
+        TENANT_CONTEXT.remove();
+    }
+}
+```
+
+**依赖项**: `JwtUtil.java` 需新增 `getTenantIdFromToken(String token)` 方法
+
+---
+
+### 层级二：JWT Token 扩展
+
+**目标文件**: `backend/src/main/java/com/ams/utils/JwtUtil.java`
+
+```java
+/**
+ * 从Token中提取租户ID
+ * @param token JWT Token
+ * @return tenant_id 或 null
+ */
+public static Long getTenantIdFromToken(String token) {
+    Claims claims = getClaimsFromToken(token);
+    Object tenantIdClaim = claims.get("tenant_id");
+    if (tenantIdClaim == null) {
+        return null;
+    }
+    if (tenantIdClaim instanceof Integer) {
+        return ((Integer) tenantIdClaim).longValue();
+    }
+    if (tenantIdClaim instanceof Long) {
+        return (Long) tenantIdClaim;
+    }
+    return Long.parseLong(tenantIdClaim.toString());
+}
+```
+
+---
+
+### 层级三：请求过滤器层
+
+**目标文件**: `backend/src/main/java/com/ams/config/JwtAuthenticationFilter.java`
+
+```java
+@Override
+protected void doFilterInternal(HttpServletRequest request, 
+                                HttpServletResponse response, 
+                                FilterChain filterChain) 
+        throws ServletException, IOException {
+    try {
+        String token = extractToken(request);
+        if (token != null) {
+            // 设置用户上下文
+            Authentication auth = jwtUtil.getAuthentication(token);
+            SecurityContextHolder.getContext().setAuthentication(auth);
+            
+            // 【新增】设置租户上下文
+            TenantContextHolder.setFromToken(token);
+        }
+        filterChain.doFilter(request, response);
+    } finally {
+        // 【必须】请求结束时清理 ThreadLocal
+        TenantContextHolder.clear();
+        SecurityContextHolder.clearContext();
+    }
+}
+```
+
+---
+
+### 层级四：AOP 强制校验切面
+
+**目标文件**: `backend/src/main/java/com/ams/aspect/TenantIsolationAspect.java`
+
+```java
+package com.ams.aspect;
+
+import com.ams.context.TenantContextHolder;
+import com.ams.exception.TenantSecurityException;
+import org.aspectj.lang.JoinPoint;
+import org.aspectj.lang.annotation.Aspect;
+import org.aspectj.lang.annotation.Before;
+import org.springframework.core.annotation.Order;
+import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;
+
+/**
+ * 租户隔离切面
+ * 所有 @TenantSensitive 注解的方法强制校验租户上下文
+ */
+@Aspect
+@Component
+@Order(1) // 高优先级，在其他切面之前执行
+public class TenantIsolationAspect {
+
+    @Before("@annotation(com.ams.annotation.TenantSensitive)")
+    public void validateTenantContext(JoinPoint joinPoint) {
+        Long tenantId = TenantContextHolder.getCurrentTenantId();
+        if (tenantId == null) {
+            throw new TenantSecurityException(
+                "TENANT_CONTEXT_REQUIRED",
+                "访问租户敏感接口必须提供有效 Token"
+            );
+        }
+    }
+}
+```
+
+**注解定义**:
+```java
+package com.ams.annotation;
+
+import java.lang.annotation.*;
+
+@Target(ElementType.METHOD)
+@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
+@Documented
+public @interface TenantSensitive {
+    // 标记方法需要租户上下文校验
+}
+```
+
+---
+
+### 层级五：Repository 层隔离
+
+**目标文件**: `backend/src/main/java/com/ams/repository/AssetRepository.java`
+
+```java
+package com.ams.repository;
+
+import com.ams.entity.Asset;
+import org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository;
+import org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.Query;
+import org.springframework.data.repository.query.Param;
+import org.springframework.stereotype.Repository;
+
+import java.util.List;
+import java.util.Optional;
+
+/**
+ * 资产仓储层
+ * 所有查询强制携带租户ID过滤
+ */
+@Repository
+public interface AssetRepository extends JpaRepository<Asset, Long> {
+    
+    /**
+     * 按租户ID查询资产列表
+     * @param tenantId 租户ID（从安全上下文注入，禁止从请求参数获取）
+     */
+    @Query("SELECT a FROM Asset a WHERE a.tenantId = :tenantId")
+    List<Asset> findByTenantId(@Param("tenantId") Long tenantId);
+    
+    /**
+     * 按ID和租户ID查询（防越权）
+     */
+    @Query("SELECT a FROM Asset a WHERE a.id = :id AND a.tenantId = :tenantId")
+    Optional<Asset> findByIdAndTenantId(@Param("id") Long id, 
+                                        @Param("tenantId") Long tenantId);
+    
+    /**
+     * 更新资产（强制租户校验）
+     */
+    @Query("UPDATE Asset a SET a.name = :name WHERE a.id = :id AND a.tenantId = :tenantId")
+    int updateByIdAndTenantId(@Param("id") Long id, 
+                              @Param("name") String name,
+                              @Param("tenantId") Long tenantId);
+}
+```
+
+---
+
+### 层级六：Service 层集成
+
+**目标文件**: `backend/src/main/java/com/ams/service/impl/AssetServiceImpl.java`
+
+```java
+package com.ams.service.impl;
+
+import com.ams.context.TenantContextHolder;
+import com.ams.entity.Asset;
+import com.ams.exception.ResourceNotFoundException;
+import com.ams.exception.TenantSecurityException;
+import com.ams.repository.AssetRepository;
+import com.ams.service.AssetService;
+import lombok.RequiredArgsConstructor;
+import org.springframework.stereotype.Service;
+import org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional;
+
+import java.util.List;
+
+@Service
+@RequiredArgsConstructor
+public class AssetServiceImpl implements AssetService {
+    
+    private final AssetRepository assetRepository;
+    
+    @Override
+    public List<Asset> listAssets() {
+        Long tenantId = TenantContextHolder.getCurrentTenantId();
+        return assetRepository.findByTenantId(tenantId);
+    }
+    
+    @Override
+    public Asset getAsset(Long assetId) {
+        Long tenantId = TenantContextHolder.getCurrentTenantId();
+        return assetRepository.findByIdAndTenantId(assetId, tenantId)
+            .orElseThrow(() -> new ResourceNotFoundException("Asset", assetId));
+    }
+    
+    @Override
+    @Transactional
+    public Asset createAsset(Asset asset) {
+        Long tenantId = TenantContextHolder.getCurrentTenantId();
+        asset.setTenantId(tenantId); // 自动注入租户ID
+        return assetRepository.save(asset);
+    }
+    
+    @Override
+    @Transactional
+    public Asset updateAsset(Long assetId, Asset updateData) {
+        Long tenantId = TenantContextHolder.getCurrentTenantId();
+        Asset asset = assetRepository.findByIdAndTenantId(assetId, tenantId)
+            .orElseThrow(() -> new TenantSecurityException(
+                "TENANT_MISMATCH",
+                "无权操作其他租户的资产"
+            ));
+        
+        // 更新非租户字段
+        asset.setName(updateData.getName());
+        return assetRepository.save(asset);
+    }
+}
+```
+
+---
+
+### 层级七：Controller 层
+
+**目标文件**: `backend/src/main/java/com/ams/controller/AssetController.java`
+
+```java
+package com.ams.controller;
+
+import com.ams.annotation.TenantSensitive;
+import com.ams.entity.Asset;
+import com.ams.service.AssetService;
+import lombok.RequiredArgsConstructor;
+import org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity;
+import org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.*;
+
+import java.util.List;
+
+@RestController
+@RequestMapping("/api/assets")
+@RequiredArgsConstructor
+public class AssetController {
+    
+    private final AssetService assetService;
+    
+    @GetMapping
+    @TenantSensitive  // 强制租户校验
+    public ResponseEntity<List<Asset>> listAssets() {
+        return ResponseEntity.ok(assetService.listAssets());
+    }
+    
+    @GetMapping("/{id}")
+    @TenantSensitive
+    public ResponseEntity<Asset> getAsset(@PathVariable Long id) {
+        return ResponseEntity.ok(assetService.getAsset(id));
+    }
+    
+    @PostMapping
+    @TenantSensitive
+    public ResponseEntity<Asset> createAsset(@RequestBody Asset asset) {
+        // 注意: 不接收 tenantId 参数，自动从安全上下文获取
+        return ResponseEntity.ok(assetService.createAsset(asset));
+    }
+    
+    @PutMapping("/{id}")
+    @TenantSensitive
+    public ResponseEntity<Asset> updateAsset(@PathVariable Long id, 
+                                             @RequestBody Asset asset) {
+        return ResponseEntity.ok(assetService.updateAsset(id, asset));
+    }
+}
+```
